User manual for Hangman game.
This game has been produced by Tynan, Nicole and Pedro

What is the goal of the game?
The goal of this game is to be able to guess characters of the word from the number of spaces shown. The spaces shown are how many 
characters are in the word. Incorrect guesses cause you to loose a life (text based game, if GUI then when hangman is hung) and the game 
is lost when there are no lives next. A correct guess of the word causes you to progress to the next level.

How do i play?
Hangman is played by guessing the characters in the word shown. This is done by pressing the letter you would like to guess when prompted.

